      "end_time": 8280.0,
      "text": "Topic: Convex lens."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 10200.0,
      "end_time": 12360.0,
      "text": "Can a magnifying glass burn paper?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14600.0,
      "end_time": 16420.0,
      "text": "I think you have gone nuts."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16800.0,
      "end_time": 17300.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17500.0,
      "end_time": 18800.0,
      "text": "It is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 18800.0,
      "end_time": 19400.0,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 19660.0,
      "end_time": 20660.0,
      "text": "But how?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 20900.0,
      "end_time": 24360.0,
      "text": "It is because a magnifying glass is actually a convex lens."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 24680.0,
      "end_time": 28100.0,
      "text": "A convex lens is thicker in the middle and thinner at the edges."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 29220.0,
      "end_time": 30240.0,
      "text": "Like a fish?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 30720.0,
      "end_time": 31940.0,
      "text": "Absolutely."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 32840.0,
      "end_time": 36960.0,
      "text": "This shape of the convex lens makes the parallel rays of sunlight to refract."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 36960.0,
      "end_time": 39520.0,
      "text": "Such that they converge or come together at a point."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 40560.0,
      "end_time": 43200.0,
      "text": "So, when they come together, do they have a party?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 44460.0,
      "end_time": 45540.0,
      "text": "Please listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45820.0,
      "end_time": 51680.0,
      "text": "As the rays converge, the concentration of sunlight at that point increases, thus producing heat."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 51920.0,
      "end_time": 55900.0,
      "text": "This heat starts a fire which eventually causes the paper to burn."
    },
